oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.partition

Class PartitioningResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.geojson.FeatureCollection
      • oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.partition.PartitioningResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PartitioningResult
extends FeatureCollection
    Object representation of a GeoJSON partitioning result file. A file of this type is generated by a partitioning jon such as Partitioning or Partitioning.
    Contained features represent individual partitions. Each feature contains a field name FEATURE_PROPS_ELEM_COUNT which is the number of elements in the partition.
    Author:
    hsaucedo
